Description: Comprehensive controller identification tool for GOcontroll Moduline
 Displays controller hardware info, installed go-* tool versions, Ethernet,
 WiFi/Bluetooth, 4G modem (SIM7600G), CAN interfaces, and installed module
 firmware with release dates from the GOcontroll cloud.

